metadata.name: Mosaico #1 - Cinquecento
metadata.description:
Title: Cinquecento
Location: Favignana Island |  Sicily | Italy
Year: 2022
Size: 6285 x 6763 @ 600 DPI | 15.70 MB

I have spent ten years chasing perfection, details and extreme resolution.

With this collection I want to go back to the basics of photography and appreciate it as a moment forever trapped in Polaroids.

In Mosaico, many individual stories live in frames and come together with an overall story of that precise place at that moment with a surreal visual result.
